The core grafit application should _not_ use wx directly
but only the grafit.gui toolkit.
grafit.gui contains all the calls to the toolkit (wx, qt, whatever), so:

grafit.gui provides 
-------------------

- the basic controls:
    - Button
    - List
    - Combo
    - Label
    - Entry

- special controls
    - GLView
    - Table
    - Shell

- layout containers:
    - Box
    - Grid

- main window and panels
    - Window
    - MainWindow
